rse, and see them bring miracles (or totally innocent CAT'astrophes) to your work.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join us now! You can already spend hours and hours as an esteemed Nekokami Planetary Architect in our Early Access:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840890/extras/ffbe1035e806a10e63b2621f6fc6bf2d.avif?t=1772367028\" width=1560 height=231 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840890/extras/db8669d366cb6a3c0ca52b9abb215e0c.avif?t=1772367028\" width=1560 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840890/extras/ecf791fa491ccf204bfb0832d3638866.avif?t=1772367028\" width=1560 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We repeat again: the Universe of Nekokami is thoroughly, totally inhibited by Cats. Your colleagues are Cats. You seem to be a Cat. Even the gods and spirits (the Kami*) roaming among the stars are Cats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 Your Cat colleagues can be found working on all sorts of environments and biomes over the Milky Way. <u>Every one of the 30 Star Systems is a world of its own!</u> Don't worry, your Cat colleagues probably don't completely get what they are doing as well. You can always experiment at your own pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2840890/extras/5f9a94ee3be8f395